-- ComplexNumber/series.math
--
-- The algebra of partial sums on ℂ, mirroring Real/series.math:
-- pointwise rewriting, linearity (sums, negation, differences, scalar
-- factors on either side), and the window bound against the real
-- series of moduli. `ComplexNumber.partialSum` itself (and its
-- coordinate bridges and splitting lemma) lives with the exponential,
-- in ComplexNumber/exponential.math.

